comments: Vanderbilt (MIN) makes contact with Durant's (BKN) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Vanderbilt (MIN) gathers the ball on his right foot and comes to a legal jump stop.
Durant (BKN) makes marginal contact with Vanderbilt's (MIN) off-arm as he contests his shot attempt at the basket.
Durant (BKN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Reid (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (BKN) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Aldridge (BKN) places his hand to Edwards' (MIN) side after his gather and marginal contact occurs.
Durant (BKN) pushes Reid (MIN) with two hands and affects his ability to defend the pass.
Mills (BKN) and Russell (MIN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Reid (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (BKN) path and makes marginal contact as roll toward the basket.
Reid (MIN) makes marginal contact to Harden (BKN) as they pursue the loose ball and disengages.
Edwards (MIN) intentionally kicks the ball.
Beasley (MIN) places his arm to Harden's front after his gather and makes contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Reid (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Mills' (BKN) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Reid (MIN) and Aldridge (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Johnson (BKN) places his hand momentarily on Beasley (MN) and the contact is marginal.
Vanderbilt (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Durant's (BKN) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Aldridge (BKN) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Harden (BKN) briefly places his hand against Reid's (MIN) hip before correcting.
Russell (MIN) briefly places his hands on Mills (BKN) and releases as he goes in the opposite direction.  He does not extend into Mills and dislodge him from his position.
Durant (BKN) and Russell (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
